Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:05.23,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,29th Suimei University of the Arts \NHigh School Graduation Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.53,0:00:07.37,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, everything's fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:10.86,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}#23 Graduation Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:09.38,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,We're waiting for you, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:10.86,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:12.65,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,How did yours go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.03,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:18.51,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's our last time wearing our uniforms...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:21.06,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you getting horny?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:24.44,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Do you want to cop \Na feel one last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:25.68,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:28.04,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. After all, it's good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.27,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:31.54,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to say no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:35.63,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I didn't realize you \Ncouldn't handle boldness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:38.10,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind later, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:39.43,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Please take one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:41.12,Saku-main,GIRL A,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:43.12,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:44.06,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Please take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:45.48,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Pin it on your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:46.02,Saku-overlap,GIRL B,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:47.14,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What are these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:47.83,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:48.85,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:49.36,Saku-overlap,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:51.40,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry blossoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:53.51,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What are they? Brooches?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:56.40,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,What? You mean you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.40,0:00:59.67,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was Sakura Hall's idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.67,0:01:01.15,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall's?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:03.22,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:06.30,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No matter the hurry you're in,\Nyou have to stop at red lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:07.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Even now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:12.92,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Since we have a spare minute, \NI made these for everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:15.22,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:17.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Rita, what are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:20.37,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that cherry\N blossoms are important...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:21.76,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Japanese at departures.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:25.00,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought it'd be nice if \Nall the students of Suimei...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:26.81,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,could wear the same flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.79,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,on their chests for the \Ngraduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.79,0:01:29.57,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:31.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There's enough for every student?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:33.18,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was Ryunosuke's idea—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:35.61,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,At the former freeloader's request,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:37.66,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had the Student Council make \Nthe necessary arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:40.35,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,They should have already been distributed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:43.72,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing. Thanks, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:46.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's going to be wearing \Ncherry blossoms, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:47.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:48.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:51.00,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:52.43,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:53.47,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:54.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:55.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:01:56.50,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:02.47,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Graduating students, please enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:21.15,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}A school painted by the four seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:28.99,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Our heartbeats resonate with youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:33.70,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ah, my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:37.28,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:45.73,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}are as bright and clear as the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:49.69,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Graduation Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:53.94,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ah, looking up at the sky, \Nwe see the distant future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:58.61,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Suimei, Suimei,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:05.30,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Suimei High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:18.03,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke, your lack of exercise \Nhas caught up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:19.60,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.92,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think they'll still let us inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:25.73,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Graduation ceremonies are boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:28.01,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Listening from out here is just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:30.97,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.29,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.98,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't enjoy the melancholy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:39.94,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Ponytail's already \Ncrying her eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.00,Saku-main,PRESIDENT,0000,0000,0000,,I met...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:45.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the upperclassmen for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:47.80,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,at the new student welcoming ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:50.83,Saku-main,PRESIDENT,0000,0000,0000,,I was nervous at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:55.38,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but they gave me a warm \Nwelcome right from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:03:59.22,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.03,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,When I had nowhere to go, they...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:11.73,Saku-main,PRESIDENT,0000,0000,0000,,We will continue to protect \Nthe spirit of Suimei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:14.02,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that you have handed down to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:17.70,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.15,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,couldn't protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:29.05,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Once the graduation ceremony \Nends, Sakura Hall will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:32.66,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the color of cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:40.34,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Next, a response from the graduating \Nstudent representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.05,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The graduating student representative:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:45.13,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiigusa Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:47.01,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.47,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Kamiigusa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.06,Saku-main,PRINCIPAL,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why isn't it Tatebayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:57.23,Saku-main,VP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:10.51,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,As though encouraged by \Nthe warm spring sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:15.87,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,even the hard buds of the cherry \Nblossoms have slowly begun to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:21.28,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,On this day that infuses our \Nskin with the new season,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:28.59,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we, the third years, are \Ngrateful that we can graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:35.18,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to apply to Suimei \Nin order to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:40.59,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,In middle school, I didn't have \Nanyone I could call a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:45.35,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,But if I came to this school...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:46.94,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Suimei University of the Arts High School
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:46.94,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Application Information
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:49.57,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,My former teacher \Nenthusiastically recommended...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:54.06,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that I apply to Suimei, \Nbelieving I might find friends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:06:01.62,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,And I really did make some precious friends \Nin my three years at Suimei High.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:04.84,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,And what helped me find \Nthese new friends was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:08.42,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall, the student dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.38,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I was kicked out of the regular dorms...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:15.30,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,within a week of starting school...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:17.31,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and moved into Sakura Hall by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:22.39,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,At first, it was a depressing place with \Nonly the supervising teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:24.07,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-sensei, and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:30.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,My high school life started in a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:33.85,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with no laughter or conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:38.16,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The first night I moved into Sakura Hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:42.15,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked in each of the empty rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:45.21,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,and I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:51.31,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream was for all of Sakura \NHall's rooms to be filled,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:56.64,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and for days full of warm light \Nand laughter to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.94,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Someone heard my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:08.54,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,One by one, the empty \Nrooms began to fill...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:11.26,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,People would say "good \Nmorning" in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:13.57,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and "I'm home" when they returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:16.77,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,When someone came home,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.30,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,they were greeted with a "welcome back."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.73,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy, it almost frightened me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:28.59,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The dream I had when I first \Narrived at Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.22,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,had finally come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:33.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:36.62,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:42.23,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,In particular, this last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:45.90,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,has been a chain of events I \Ncould only describe as a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.72,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I made new friends this spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:54.19,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The hotpot parties we \Nthrew for special events,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:56.53,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,only two or three times \Nin previous years,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.63,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,became more and more frequent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:03.54,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, there were times when \Nwe were eating hotpot every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:08.29,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Every time we gathered \Naround that pot to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:11.22,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered if this was what \Nhappiness tasted like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:12.93,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:17.30,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Over the summer, we sneaked \Ninto the school pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.99,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Playing in our swimsuits,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:23.23,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,getting caught by the security \Nguard, and running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:28.26,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone kept up with me \Nas I ran ahead of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:33.40,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget the fireworks \Nthat exploded above us that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:37.49,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'll never forget them either...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.99,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,At the culture festival in the fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:44.18,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall put together \Nan interactive show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.86,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I had only wished for friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.48,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had never even considered...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:55.26,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,working together with \Nothers to make something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:09:03.01,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Milky Way Cat Nyapollon is the most \Nwonderful thing I have ever created...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.52,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,and the greatest work of Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.83,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,In the winter, we had \Nsome disagreements,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:16.32,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and our relationships became strained.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:21.54,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Our days weren't always so sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:25.04,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,There were times when \Nwe tried to run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:27.64,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and abandon everything \Nbecause it hurt so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.80,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,But, because of those rainy days,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:34.63,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe the small seeds \Nof emotion sprouted...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.55,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and bloomed into new relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:43.95,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:49.53,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I know you've always \Nworked hard to support us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:52.76,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,without placing any burdens on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:56.80,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You are like a sister and a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.74,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You are my beloved teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.62,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:07.87,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I loved your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:08.83,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It was love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:11.72,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Since the very beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:14.82,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you looked at me the same way \Nyou looked at everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.91,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can always be proud...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:19.96,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,of the me that I see in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:23.47,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron, I look up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:25.42,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:27.36,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nanamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:33.01,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Since you provided voice \Nacting for my work,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:38.20,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hoped you would become \Nthe last member of Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:42.93,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You made my wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:44.33,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.25,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.93,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You've been hurt by your \Nprevious friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:54.52,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You do everything you can \Nto shield your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:11:00.63,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,There were times I felt \Nyou and I were the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:04.45,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You are my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:10.65,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel the same way about \Nme, even a little, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:20.39,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue being \Nfriends with Rittan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.54,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, kouhai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:28.87,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You always listened to \Neverything I had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:32.50,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You even stayed up all night \Nplaying games with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:39.03,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I did to you, \Nyou never left my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:44.47,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It made me so happy, I couldn't \Ncontain my excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:48.00,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for all the \Ntrouble I've caused you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.73,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,To everyone I've met at Suimei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:56.98,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,To all the teachers who supported me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:00.85,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and all the people who live in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:05.53,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:13.83,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,To the best friends I made at Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:17.04,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to leave you with these words...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:26.51,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for staying with \Nme until this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:30.77,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you more than words can express!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:38.94,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,With both my hands full \Nof happiness, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I graduate from Suimei High.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.41,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:58.88,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall is currently in \Ndanger of being torn down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:07.64,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let them tear \Ndown our beloved Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.89,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Lend us your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:13.56,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:17.27,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take our Sakura Hall away from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:19.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:25.82,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Don't take our \NSakura Hall away from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:28.98,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:34.04,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She hadn't given up yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:38.38,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Lend us your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:39.84,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:43.63,Saku-main,PRINCIPAL,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:45.59,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you can say whatever you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.92,Saku-main,PRINCIPAL,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? \NReturn to your seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.76,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,We're not just doing as we please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:54.26,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Principal, you know that \Nthe response speech...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:14:01.07,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,at the Suimei High graduation ceremony \Nis given by the top student.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:03.00,Saku-main,PRINCIPAL,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but no one said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.70,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you could use the response \Nto make a personal statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.20,Saku-main,PRINCIPAL,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.01,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but the former Student Council President \NTatebayashi should be the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.78,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,But we turned in our manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:14.76,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Tatebayashi-kun should have discussed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:17.09,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,changing the manuscript \Nwith you this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.92,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, since it's such \Nan important document,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:24.25,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Response
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:23.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you don't mean to say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:27.03,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you couldn't be bothered to read it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:28.16,Saku-main,PRINCIPAL,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.27,Saku-main,PRINCIPAL,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:33.02,Saku-main,PRINCIPAL,0000,0000,0000,,Get her off the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:33.68,Saku-main,TEACHERS,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.02,Saku-main,TEACHERS,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.31,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiigusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.08,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,Get down from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:39.91,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:41.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:47.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who are grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:48.45,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:49.24,Saku-main,TEACHERS,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:53.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I felt so anxious when I was \Nkicked out of the regular dorms,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:56.45,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but you created a place where I belonged!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:58.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A place called Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:14:59.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.37,Saku-main,TEACHERS,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, Kanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:02.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.13,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:04.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:05.59,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:08.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:11.34,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happened, \Nyou always bore the brunt of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:15.60,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,When I was lost, you always \Ndragged me into taking action!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:17.52,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.52,Saku-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.48,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I love Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:23.02,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take away our Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:27.07,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nanamin, Mashiron...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.86,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Show 'em, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.80,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I know Sakura Hall can do more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:33.62,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Miyahara-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:36.12,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:36.12,Saku-overlap,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, give them hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:39.00,Saku-main,SHIHO,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shiina-san, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.47,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:43.08,Saku-main,BOY 1,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.17,Saku-main,BOY 2,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.57,Saku-main,GIRL 1,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:47.00,Saku-main,BOY 3,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way, Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.63,Saku-main,BOY 4,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:16:07.02,Saku-main,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall! Sakura Hall! Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:09.86,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't gather enough signatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:12.86,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.33,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:24.20,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We just got through to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:29.50,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for doing this \Nat your graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:33.82,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not just Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:39.63,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone at Suimei is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:43.35,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:46.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could have spent \Nmore time with you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:48.20,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:50.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could have done \Nmore stupid stuff together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:53.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There are still a lot of \Nthings we haven't done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:56.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I don't \Nwant you to graduate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could be together forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.20,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:05.37,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You've still got a year \Nof high school left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But you guys won't be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:13.01,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,So make it even better than \Nthe year we spent together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.94,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Spend it with the all the kouhai-kuns...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:16.95,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who will be joining you next year!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:22.47,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You can do all the things with them \Nthat you weren't able to do with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.44,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,So don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.48,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rooting for you, kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:31.12,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rooting for all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:33.65,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rooting for Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:34.76,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:35.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:37.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:37.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.16,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.95,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:43.80,Saku-overlap,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's try to keep this peaceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:47.66,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Sit back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.06,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:53.13,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,You're all idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:57.01,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,This is why none of your lectures \Nare worth listening to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.30,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:59.51,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:03.14,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in here is on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:08.81,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you accept it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.12,Saku-main,PRINCIPAL,0000,0000,0000,,Tatebayashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:14.23,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Sakura Hall was \Noriginally created to nurture...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:19.28,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the talents of art students, \Nregardless of society's framework.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:22.87,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to say that the \Nproblem children of Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.75,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who cannot follow the \Nrules are necessarily right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:31.47,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But the way they are true to themselves \Nand see their own potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:35.30,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,and the strong bond they share...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:38.57,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,has made me feel jealous of Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:43.73,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'm not the only \None who has felt this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:46.56,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:49.31,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you make your decision here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:50.81,Saku-main,PRINCIPAL,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.12,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,As luck would have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:55.54,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the entire student body is in attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:19:00.54,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you support or oppose repealing the \Ndecision to tear down Sakura Hall?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:05.20,Saku-main,VP,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-Principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.76,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:09.54,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:11.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.42,Saku-overlap,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Ryunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.05,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:16.54,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Applaud if you support repealing \Nthe decision to tear down...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:18.85,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:20.26,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:38.40,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Those who support repealing the \Ndecision to tear down Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:41.70,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,throw your cherry blossoms in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.92,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:56.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.41,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look so unhappy, kouhai-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm unhappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:04.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we standing out here \Nduring the graduation ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.21,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:09.62,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be satisfied unless \NI bully Kanda-kun later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:11.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for {\i1}you{\i0} \Nto be standing out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:16.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,When did you prepare that speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.20,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:21.80,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Aoyama-san \Nwould have opposed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:23.27,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I would have!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:27.59,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I had, I think you \Nwould have done it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:28.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:31.33,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,It was an impressive plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:34.12,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Influencing people with a speech,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:37.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,showing them the incompetence \Nof the teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.88,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and conducting a vote in which \Neveryone felt compelled...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to oppose the demolition of Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:43.73,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Under those conditions, \Neven students...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:46.86,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who hadn't signed our petition \Nwould throw their flowers in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:49.93,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like \Nsome kind of awful scam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:51.25,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't just sound like one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:53.48,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it all worked out, Nanamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:57.02,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall will never be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:01.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Sakura Hall is indestructible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.03,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,Just stand there in silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:07.26,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sorata's fault we got in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:09.49,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda, keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.59,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, hush.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:13.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to \Nyell at Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:14.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:20.47,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.67,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We asked Hauhau to play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:43.24,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let's be friends forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:39.33,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they play this song at \Nelementary school graduations?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:44.86,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a wonderful song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:58.21,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let's dream of tomorrow as we \Nwalk down the path of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:13.48,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Live as freely as the \Nbirds flying in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:21.85,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Goodbye for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.85,0:22:28.20,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:57.95,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Treasure the joy of \Nbelieving in one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.55,0:23:06.38,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Goodbye for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:12.91,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:22.38,Saku-main,TRANSLATION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Until we meet again.
